@startuml UC_21_Manage_Notifications
title UC-21: Manage Notifications

|User|
start
:(1) Open Notifications;

|System|
:(2) Load the user's notifications;
:(3) Return the notification list;

|User|
:(4) Mark one notification or all notifications as read;
:(5) Delete a notification if needed;

|System|
:(6) Validate notification ownership;
:(7) Update read or deleted status;
:(8) Return the refreshed list;

stop
@enduml
